          <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] mb-4">
            The Alfa Laval WSB-203 is a concentrator version of the MAB-103 disc-stack centrifuge. It is specifically designed to concentrate oil from water-based industrial fluids such as <a href="/machine-coolant-centrifuge/" class="text-[#1B3A5C] underline hover:text-[#E8A317]">machine coolant</a>, <a href="/industrial-washer-fluid-centrifuge/" class="text-[#1B3A5C] underline hover:text-[#E8A317]">washer fluid, parts washer solvent</a>, water-soluble <a href="/cutting-oil-centrifuge/" class="text-[#1B3A5C] underline hover:text-[#E8A317]">cutting oils</a>, <a href="/waste-oil-emulsion-centrifuge/" class="text-[#1B3A5C] underline hover:text-[#E8A317]">de-oiling of split emulsions</a>, etc.
          </p>
